        </div>
        <div class="break-inside-avoid">
          <img class="w-full rounded-lg" src="/images/community/08.jpeg" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8 my-16">
    <h2
      class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-4xl text-pretty text-center text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950 sm:text-3xl"
    >
      Redefine Finance Together: <span class="theme-gradient">Join Wahine Community</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-4xl text-pretty text-center text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 sm:text-2xl">
      Join us as we forge a new era in finance, where every woman's voice is heard, every ambition is supported, and
      every success story inspires the next generation of female financial leaders. Together, we're not just breaking
      barriers – we're creating a legacy of empowerment, excellence, and enduring impact in the world of finance.
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-6 mb-10">
      <a
        href="https://forms.gle/W9pvgTJy4BQtLs5s6"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-medium transition-colors"
      >
        Join Our Community
        <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
